msgctxt "72_Zhao"
msgid "Hey, Ma-chan. We have a customer waiting for you."
msgstr "Hola, Ma-chan. Hay una cliente que te está esperando."

msgctxt "84_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah? Who is it?"
msgstr "¿Ah sí? ¿Quién es?"

msgctxt "96_Zhao"
msgid "A Filipino girl. She says she has a favor to ask. Will you at least hear her out?"
msgstr "Una chica filipina. Dice que quiere pedirte un favor. \\r ¿Podrías escucharla por lo menos?"

msgctxt "108_Tanimura"
msgid "...All right. I'll head on over."
msgstr "...De acuerdo. Allá voy."

